Use the standard library
This is how to decode_cyclic of s:
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that i is 1
  Do this s's length times:
    When i is less than s's length, then:
      Add result to item i in s
      Increase i
    But, if not:
      Add result to item 0 in s
    End when
  End do
  The answer is result
Now you know